  "short_description": "What the enemy can do, you can do as well! Activate the \"Override\" system and and hijack enemy Cyborgs on the fly during high-intensity battles. Mix and match the Cyborgs you seized with fully customizable \"Extensions\" and \"Cores\", and craft hundreds of game-breaking combat builds!",
